Quickstrike:



Quickstrike saw Drill Bit, a danger, over him. He slashed out his 
cobra arm, jabbing his venomeous fangs into his leg. He let go when 
He fired on him again. He lifted his legs up to support him, scurring 
backwards for a few seconds, then fell back down.

His head went light, and his vision started to blurr.

> ::DrillBit::
> 
> He sees the bot having trouble. He gets closer. He stands over him.
> He gets down to the floor., he points his gattaling gun right at
> Quickstrike's face. His barrels only a centimeter from Quickstrike's
> face. He fires ruthlesly.
